mahakavi kalidasu ( telugu : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1960 telugu biographical film based on the life of poet poet kalidas , produced by p. adinarayana rao on &lt;unk&gt; productions banner and directed by &lt;unk&gt; rao . starring akkineni nageswara rao , savitri in the lead roles and music composed by pendyala nageswara rao .